data.description: Welcome to 947 Pinnacle Club in prestigious Courtyards at Pinnacle Estates! This 2-3 bedroom, 2-full bath free standing home perfectly blends modern, single-story living with classic elegance. The open floor plan features large rooms, high ceilings, LOTS of natural light, and a gorgeous gourmet kitchen with island seating. The primary suite offers a generous walk-in closet, double sinks and zero threshold walk in shower! The private outdoor entertaining area is complimented by additional green space behind the property. Enjoy convenient walkable access to Pinnacle Golf Club and Cimi's Bistro, live the lifestyle you deserve with quick access to I-71 and downtown Columbus!
